  - ⚠️ Business logic and UI fully entangled — no testable function boundaries (ISS-006, TD-002)
  - ℹ️ Implicit else branch silently covers Divide — fragile if selectbox options grow (ISS-001)
  - ℹ️ No session state, no calculation history (ISS-009)
